desc: Bringing to life cozy functional spaces. A female-owned Canadian business building handmade wooden furniture and home decor. High-quality Walnut, Cedar, Oak, Cherry, Maple, Douglas Fir and Pine are our most commonly used woods. The best part? Every piece designed is completely customizable. We accept custom orders.

layout.text: Hand-Crafted Home Furnishings Serving Carstairs, Sylvan Lake, Calgary, And Surrounding Areas
